ADF Pipeline — pipeline_agri_etl

Trigger: Daily scheduled trigger (configurable) + event-based trigger on new file arrival
#Activities:
1.Copy Activity — Ingests raw CSV/Excel from source into Azure Blob Storage
2.Data Flow — Applies transformation logic (type casting, null handling, column derivation)
3.Stored Procedure Activity — Loads cleaned data into Azure SQL staging table
4.Validation Activity — Checks row counts before proceeding

Power BI Auto-Refresh
1.Connected to Azure SQL via On-premises Data Gateway
2.Refresh triggered automatically on ADF pipeline success via Power BI REST API (called from ADF Web Activity)
3.Scheduled fallback refresh also configured in Power BI Service

Dashboard Features
1.Interactive slicers — filter by date, product, and region
2.Dynamic KPI cards — instant snapshot of revenue vs. target
3.Drill-through pages — deep-dive from summary to detail views
4.Time intelligence — MoM, YoY comparisons via DAX
5.Clean star schema data model — optimised relationships for performance
